event.title: traversed the Cuesta Grade into the valley in 1776

data.event: The de Anza Expedition traversed the Cuesta Grade into the valley in 1776.
The Santa Margarita de Cortona Asistencia was founded circa 1775, and was named for the Italian Saint, Santa Margarita de Cortona.
